Christmas with the Rat Pack is a budget-priced compilation that cobbles 
together miscellaneous tracks recorded separately by Frank Sinatra, Dean 
Martin, and Sammy Davis, Jr. Among the 16 cuts are "Silver Bells," "Rudolph 
the Red Nosed Reindeer," "Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow!," and 
"Winter Wonderland." While this material has been lifted from separate
